description: Google Calendar is a web-based application that allows users to schedule and organize events, appointments, and reminders, synchronizing across multiple devices.
name: googleCalendar
title: Google Calendar

properties.label: Start date

properties.description: Event types to return.
properties.name: eventType
properties.label: Event type

properties.description: Maximum number of events returned on one result page. The number of events in the resulting page may be less than this value, or none at all, even if there are more events matching the query. Incomplete pages can be detected by a non-empty nextPageToken field in the response.
properties.name: maxResults
properties.label: Max results

properties.description: Free text search terms to find events that match these terms in the following fields: summary, description, location, attendee's displayName, attendee's email, workingLocationProperties.officeLocation.buildingId, workingLocationProperties.officeLocation.deskId, workingLocationProperties.officeLocation.label and workingLocationProperties.customLocation.label
properties.name: q
properties.label: Search terms

properties.description: Upper bound (exclusive) for an event's start time to filter by. The default is not to filter by start time. Must be an RFC3339 timestamp with mandatory time zone offset, for example, 2011-06-03T10:00:00-07:00, 2011-06-03T10:00:00Z. Milliseconds may be provided but are ignored.
properties.name: timeMax
properties.label: Time max

properties.description: Lower bound (exclusive) for an event's end time to filter by. The default is not to filter by end time. Must be an RFC3339 timestamp with mandatory time zone offset, for example, 2011-06-03T10:00:00-07:00, 2011-06-03T10:00:00Z. Milliseconds may be provided but are ignored.
properties.name: timeMin
properties.label: Time min
